{"tid":559774,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[情人節呈獻]《煙花應該和誰看》廣東話主題曲","createTime":"2018-02-13T13:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T03:01:18.000Z","uid":171602,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"27ceb9effd41b6d477598b33243b0b7869cb1bdc","tid":559774,"uid":171602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:06:14.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟而家學緊填詞，之前睇完《煙花應該和誰看》用年度之歌幫佢寫左首主題曲，想向各位巴絲請教下點樣寫得好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 真。新手，唔岩聽屌得細力D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，女朋友仔呢首歌都係送比你，如果你見到呢個post嘅話，我想同你講其實我真係好愛你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n打上花火主題曲<br />\n調寄 : 年度之歌謝安琪<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtuberepeater.com/watch?v=JDdXRpZEfPo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtuberepeater.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJDdXRpZEfPo&d=juZNQ8TWd%2FZKTWwpyWEy8gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=d49754d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtuberepeater.com/watch?v=JDdXRpZEfPo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明天再別的優雅 流星再會的轉化<br />\n如可自成一角     再化為磚瓦   細看天邊浮華<br />\n<br />\n良辰美景   晝夜輕撫結他<br />\n凝視昨天   海裡沖出細沙<br />\n還是那天  戲言的說話<br />\n像突然地說吧     暗暗偷偷記掛<br />\n                      <br />\n還剩下了幾多花火  當空間交錯<br />\n給你最耀眼的星河<br />\n來日就使   得一首闕歌<br />\n就來給我倆踏過<br />\n<br />\n如若共你  鄉村診所   有過的苦楚<br />\n我看著 你離座<br />\n因此我  都也會做錯 <br />\n不知我   失去了甚麼<br />\n<br />\n明天再別的優雅 流星再次的轉化<br />\n人生是埸興替  珍惜著心機    不忍放棄<br />\n還剩下了幾多花火  當空間交錯<br />\n給你最耀眼的星河 <br />\n讓我看清你傷心痛楚<br />\n共同都也去度過<br />\n<br />\n如若共你  鄉村山坡  再次的花火   <br />\n我帶著你同坐<br />\n單車裡  得到了自我<br />\n捉緊你  不會有甚麼<br />\n<br />\n如若共你  幾許風波  冷冷的花火   <br />\n我要陪你捱餓<br />\n不緊要   不快也會度過<br />\n班房裡  失去了甚麼<br />\n<br />\n黃昏掛著的天梯    留給是誰的婚禮<br />\n時空突然枯萎   但仍存美麗   心裡一生長攜<br />\n乘著列車  路遙衝出鐵軌<br />\n流入海中     二人雙雙 跌低<br />\n凝望背影   淡然的說誓 <br />\n寂寞留在心底    我想輕吻  過世<br />\n<br />\n明月似畫   水中天上   突然一吻  到底"},{"pid":"213f9c47269d38af1fad088cf86979892e825fbb","tid":559774,"uid":171602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cc9c827dd86af68824b0a3f2eecac2e434c56c","tid":559774,"uid":171602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79eb62533048107902318eae0d6c60bf9da33beb","tid":559774,"uid":171602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9009f5890bd05d087c99fe9135017bdfc8e56f","tid":559774,"uid":103754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea60b689261726bb8d9fc97d55e8223d71cd7b5f","tid":559774,"uid":103754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:58:38.000Z","msg":"好似寫得幾好，幫推"},{"pid":"769fdf2392fd22de5b8a74f650c60d896798cf7f","tid":559774,"uid":7275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7d80cc91da006cdea81aa783db4ebaa7cc3876","tid":559774,"uid":103754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T14:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a32ab6293b2